OL,10,G0230 Father Brown
OL,11,     FWhen collector Brander Merton
OL,12,     Facquires a rare Coptic chalice,
OL,13,     Frumours swirl about its dark past.
OL,14,     FAfter a sudden death, Father Brown
OL,15,     Fis drawn into a mystery where
OL,16,     Fsuperstition and truth collide.
